OL,3,CArsonist who killed pensioner in
OL,4,C'random' house fire guilty of murder
OL,6,FAn arsonist who targeted the house of
OL,7,Fan elderly couple "utterly randomly"
OL,8,Fand set a fire that left a man dead
OL,9,Fhas been found guilty of murder.
OL,11,FAndrew Gorrell, 54, was wearing a
OL,12,FNightmare on Elm Street T-shirt, a
OL,13,Fhorror film in which the central
OL,14,Fcharacter was burned alive, when he
OL,15,Fset a fire outside the Wednesbury home
OL,16,Fof John and Doreen Edwards in the
OL,17,Fearly hours of May 11 last year, a
OL,18,Ftrial at Wolverhampton Crown Court
OL,19,Fheard.
