OL,3,CArsonist who killed pensioner in
OL,4,C'random' house fire guilty of murder
OL,6,FGorrell, from Saltney in Flintshire,
OL,7,FWales, had no known links to the
OL,8,FEdwards family, their house or the
OL,9,FWednesbury area.
OL,11,FJurors took less than four hours to
OL,12,Freturn unanimous guilty verdicts to
OL,13,Fone count of murder, two counts of
OL,14,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,15,Fintent, attempting to cause grievous
OL,16,Fbodily harm with intent and arson with
OL,17,Fintent to endanger lives on Wednesday
OL,18,Fafternoon.
