OL,4,C'random' house fire guilty of murder
OL,6,FProsecution counsel Rachel Brand KC
OL,7,Ftold the jury Gorrell travelled from
OL,8,FWales and was first captured on CCTV
OL,9,Fat the Wolverhampton Central tram
OL,10,Fterminus at around 12.40am on May 11
OL,11,Fwhere he got on a tram and went to
OL,12,FWednesbury Parkway, arriving just
OL,13,Fbefore 1am.
OL,15,FHe was told to move on by staff after
OL,16,Fbeing seen loitering outside a care
OL,17,Fhome on Holyhead Road and was also
OL,18,Fseen near a school before he moved
OL,19,Fonto the Edwards' family home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/15
