OL,3,CArsonist who killed pensioner in
OL,4,C'random' house fire guilty of murder
OL,6,FMs Brand said: "He was living some
OL,7,Fconsiderable distance away. We don't
OL,8,Fknow why he came down to the West
OL,9,FMidlands on that night in May of last
OL,10,Fyear and we don't know why he was
OL,11,Fwandering around Wednesbury in the
OL,12,Fmiddle of the night. We don't know why
OL,13,Fhe decided to set a fire at the home
OL,14,Fof the Edwards family.
OL,16,F"When he was arrested and interviewed,
OL,17,Fhe made no comment to all questions
OL,18,Fpolice asked.
OL,20,F"Only the defendant can tell you why."
