OL,6,FGorrell opted not to give evidence in
OL,7,Fhis defence during the trial, but his
OL,8,Fbarrister Michael Duck KC argued that
OL,9,Fhis actions had the hallmarks of
OL,10,F"chaotic behaviour" by someone who was
OL,11,Fextremely drunk.
OL,13,FThe defendant previously admitted
OL,14,Fthree counts of arson in relation to
OL,15,Fthree separate fires he set in
OL,16,FWednesbury in the hours after the
OL,17,Ffatal house blaze, in a bin near a
OL,18,Fpub, a commercial waste bin outside a
OL,19,Fpizza takeaway and a fire in a council
OL,20,Fwaste bin in a nearby street.
