OL,6,FMs Brand said Gorrell was wearing
OL,7,F"distinctive clothing" including a
OL,8,FChicago Bulls jacket, which he was
OL,9,Falso wearing when he was arrested by
OL,10,FNorth Wales Police on May 14, and a
OL,11,FNightmare on Elm Street T-shirt.
OL,13,FOf the T-shirt, she said: "The
OL,14,Flettering said 'Nightmare on Elm
OL,15,FStreet'. Some of you may know that
OL,16,Ffilm, but for those that don't, I'm
OL,17,Ftold it's a film where one of the
OL,18,Fcentral characters was burnt to death
OL,19,Fin a fire."
