OL,6,FThe court heard a 999 call was made by
OL,7,Fa neighbour of the Edwards family at
OL,8,F3.06am on May 11 and by the time the
OL,9,Ffirst of three fire engines arrived at
OL,10,F3.14am, the wheelie bin fire had
OL,11,Fspread to the house and into the
OL,12,Fhallway.
OL,14,FJohn Edwards was semi-conscious and
OL,15,Fhad suffered severe burns to his face,
OL,16,Farms, legs and feet when he was
OL,17,Frescued from the ground floor while
OL,18,FCarl Edwards had managed to climb out
OL,19,Fof a first-floor window and into the
OL,20,Fback garden, where he was suffering
OL,21,Ffrom the effects of smoke inhalation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/15
