OL,6,FMark Edwards, who had been asleep in
OL,7,Fthe living room at the time, was found
OL,8,Fin an upstairs bedroom where he had
OL,9,Fgone to alert his parents and brother
OL,10,Fof the fire and had severe burns to
OL,11,Fhis hands, feet, face and eyes, and
OL,12,Fnearly did not survive.
OL,14,FMrs Edwards was semi-conscious and
OL,15,Fparamedics feared she would go into
OL,16,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,18,FMs Brand said: "Sadly, John Edwards
OL,19,Fdid not survive, his injuries were
OL,20,Fjust too severe.
