OL,6,F"Doctors advised his family that
OL,7,Ffurther treatment was futile and may
OL,8,Fprolong his suffering, so they were
OL,9,Fleft with really no choice but to
OL,10,Faccept that expert medical advice."
OL,12,FFire service investigators ruled out
OL,13,Fany accidental causes of the fire and
OL,14,Fconcluded it was ignition of the
OL,15,Fcontents of the wheelie bin that
OL,16,Fstarted the blaze.
