OL,6,FDuring the opening of the prosecution
OL,7,Fcase, Ms Brand told the jury of six
OL,8,Fmen and six women: "We simply ask you
OL,9,Fto remember the simple phrase `
OL,10,Factions speak louder than words.
OL,12,F"He set a fire in the middle of the
OL,13,Fnight when people were asleep. He
OL,14,Fmoved the wheelie bin and deliberately
OL,15,Fpositioned it outside the front door
OL,16,Fwhere it would cause the fire to
OL,17,Fspread, but also block the exit of
OL,18,Fanyone inside the house.
OL,26,@pD@TOUtD@AOU
