OL,3,CArsonist who killed pensioner in
OL,4,C'random' house fire guilty of murder
OL,6,F"He is a man of 54, he is not a child
OL,7,For a silly teenager. He is a mature
OL,8,Fman. The fact he moved the bin to that
OL,9,Fposition, we say, shows he intended
OL,10,Fthe occupants would be seriously
OL,11,Finjured.
OL,13,F"It was his choice to set a fire in a
OL,14,Fbin next to a house where people were
OL,15,Fasleep as opposed to setting a fire in
OL,16,Fan empty factory or an empty shop."
