OL,6,FThe Recorder of Wolverhampton, Judge
OL,7,FMichael Chambers KC, thanked the jury
OL,8,Ffor their careful deliberations in the
OL,9,Fcase, which he described as "extremely
OL,10,Fgrave".
OL,12,FHe told the defendant: "I'm adjourning
OL,13,Fyour case for sentence, it is
OL,14,Fobviously an extremely serious matter.
OL,16,F"I have to fix the minimum term, and I
OL,17,Fwill do that with the assistance of
OL,18,Fcounsel.
