OL,6,F"I am adjourning your case for a pre-
OL,7,Fsentence report and a psychiatric
OL,8,Freport. It is in your interest to
OL,9,Fcooperate with those reports.
OL,11,F"If I find out you haven't, I may well
OL,12,Fdraw an inference from that. You will
OL,13,Fbe notified of the date (for sentence)
OL,14,Fas soon as that has been agreed."
